f two opposites: and an industry that has been surprisingly been supercharged by political affiliations as well. Tesla, the world's</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1288508380/image_1288508380.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745306-rivian-is-the-ev-stock-to-hold-in-2025-not-tesla-upgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 16:31:25"}, {"id": "4745301", "title": "PeptiDream: Opulent Dream Now A Reality", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1346182684/image_1346182684.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Smiling man sleeping in a bed covered with dollars\" data-id=\"1346182684\" data-type=\"getty-image\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">tiero</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>A New Year, a New Molecule Class</h2> <p>While the cell and gene therapy industry once held much promise and allowed investors to capitalize on the great new trend in biotechnology, high costs, and stubborn IP developments have hamstrung the industry over</p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745301-peptidream-opulent-dream-now-a-reality", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 16:26:03"}, {"id": "4745321", "title": "Where Do Stocks Go From Here?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316474343/image_1316474343.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Multi exposure of abstract financial diagram on office buildings background, banking and accounting concept\" data-id=\"1316474343\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316474343/image_1316474343.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316474343/image_1